<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/head.ejs') %>

    <body>
        <header>
            <h1>Computer Vision and Autonomous Vehicles</h1>
        </header>

        <%- include('partials/nav.ejs') %>

            <main>
                
                <figure>
                    <img class="main-img" src="img/autonomous-vehicle-research-header-post-January2020.jpg"
                        alt="Bird's eye view of cars on a curved road">
                </figure>


                <div class="sections">
                    <section>
                        <h2 id="challenges">Current Challenges</h2>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Adverse Weather &amp; Lighting:</strong> rain, fog, snow, glare.</li>
                            <li><strong>Long-tail Events:</strong> rare, unpredictable edge cases.</li>
                            <li><strong>Occlusion:</strong> objects hidden behind others.</li>
                            <li><strong>Domain Shift:</strong> new cities/countries look different.</li>
                            <li><strong>Latency &amp; Compute:</strong> real-time inference on vehicle hardware.</li>
                            <li><strong>Safety &amp; Verification:</strong> proving performance at scale.</li>
                            <li><strong>Privacy &amp; Security:</strong> safeguarding data &amp; resisting attacks.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 id="mitigations">What Helps Mitigate These?</h2>
                        <table>
                            <thead>
                                <tr>
                                    <th scope="col">Challenge</th>
                                    <th scope="col">Technique</th>
                                    <th scope="col">Impact</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr>
                                    <th scope="row">Weather/Lighting</th>
                                    <td>Sensor diversity; polarization; image enhancement</td>
                                    <td>Improves robustness when vision degrades</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th scope="row">Long-tail Events</th>
                                    <td>Simulation, synthetic data, continual learning</td>
                                    <td>Exposes models to rare scenarios safely</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th scope="row">Occlusion</th>
                                    <td>Tracking + prediction; multi-view fusion</td>
                                    <td>Maintains awareness of partially hidden objects</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th scope="row">Domain Shift</th>
                                    <td>Domain adaptation; map/context priors</td>
                                    <td>Transfers performance to new geographies</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th scope="row">Latency/Compute</th>
                                    <td>Model optimization, quantization, acceleration</td>
                                    <td>Meets real-time constraints on embedded hardware</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th scope="row">Safety Assurance</th>
                                    <td>Scenario coverage, formal methods, staged rollout</td>
                                    <td>Builds evidence for reliability</td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 id="trends">Future Trends</h2>
                        <details>
                            <summary><strong>End-to-End Learning</strong></summary>
                            <p>Train perception-to-plan pipelines with safety guards.</p>
                        </details>

                        <details>
                            <summary><strong>V2X Connectivity</strong></summary>
                            <p>Cars communicate with cars/infrastructure to “see” beyond line of sight.</p>
                        </details>

                        <details>
                            <summary><strong>Edge + Cloud</strong></summary>
                            <p>Smart offloading and fleet learning improve models continuously.</p>
                        </details>

                        <details>
                            <summary><strong>Cheaper Sensors</strong></summary>
                            <p>Solid-state LiDAR & high-res radar reduce costs.</p>
                        </details>

                        <details>
                            <summary><strong>Regulatory Frameworks</strong></summary>
                            <p>Clearer testing/operations rules expand deployment zones.</p>
                        </details>
                    </section>

